title: @LosCogelones Live on KEXP from Mexico: Vive Latino is out now
Los Cogelones - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG and Vive Latino present Live on KEXP from Mexico with Los Cogelones  performing at El Desierto Casa Estudio. Recorded March 16, 2023.

Songs:
Cascabel
Mexica
Cosmos
500 años

VicogeloN Chicoei Miquiztli - Vocals, Guitar
BetogeloN Ce Cuetzpallin - Percussion, Precuauhtemics Instruments, Backing Vocals
AdrialoN Chicoace Tocht-Lee - Bass, Backing Vocals
MarckogeloN Chicoace Ollin - Drums , Backing Vocals
GabogeloN Nahui Cuauhtli - Instruments of War, Backing Vocals

KEXP Live from Mexico: Vive Latino is a partnership with Vive Latino and Indie Rocks! Magazine

Recorded at El Desierto Casa Estudio in Desierto de Los Leones, Mexico

Host: Albina Cabrera
Videographers: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro & Scott Holpainen
Video Editor: Scott Holpainen
Audio Engineers: Daniel Bitran Arizpe, Julian Martlew, JC Vertii
Audio Mixer: Fernando Urcid
Audio Mastering: Julian Martlew
Studio Assistant: Santiago Mijares 
Studio Manager: Gabriela Sandoval
Artist Coordinator (Vive Latino): Irma Celio
Audio Production Manager (Vive Latino): Paola Silva
Fixer: Danae Silva

Vive Latino:
Jordi Puig
Itzel Flores
Claudia Yannick Cabeza de Vaca
